        // branch-correct curb height: this lamp belongs to the road at arc `a`, so seat it on that branch's
        // road-surface y (p.y) — a curbside lamp on a viaduct rides the deck, one on the low road stays low.
        // hfn(bx,bz) (XZ-nearest) would drop a viaduct lamp to the ground beside/under the deck, or lift a
        // low-road lamp onto the deck at the crossing (bug 2026-07-17).
